  <summary date="2019-04-09T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Faith in Health Savings Accounts Act of 2019

This bill modifies the requirements for health savings accounts (HSAs) to treat membership in a tax-exempt health care sharing ministry as coverage under a high deductible health plan for purposes of the tax deduction for contributions to an HSA.</summary>
